Business Brief -- Telefon AB L.M. Ericsson:
   Swedish Company Confirms
   67% Drop in Pretax Profit
The group also repeated its downbeat forecast for the
current year, and said that at least the first half of the
year will be "very weak."
   "Profit for the full year is thus expected to be continued
low," Ericsson said, adding that there have been no signs of
an upturn in its main markets.